src:
Hasil Pertandingan Bournemouth vs Manchester United: Skor 1-0
02 Nov 2019, 21:31 by Bola.net
Bola.net - Manchester United (MU) mengalami antiklimaks. Setelah meraih tiga kemenangan beruntun di semua kompetisi, MU akhirnya tumbang. Bournemouth memaksa mereka pulang dengan tangan hampa.
Peringkat 7 MU menghadapi peringkat 9 Bournemouth di Vitality Stadium pada pekan ke-11 Premier League 2019/20, Sabtu (02/11/2019). MU takluk 0-1 oleh gol tunggal Joshua King di menit 45.
Dalam tiga laga sebelum ini, yang juga merupakan laga-laga tandang, MU berturut-turut mengalahkan Partizan Belgrade 1-0 di Liga Europa, Norwich City 3-1 di Premier League, dan Chelsea 2-1 di babak 16 besar Carabao Cup.
Namun, tak ada kemenangan beruntun keempat. Berikutnya, tengah pekan nanti, MU akan bermain di Liga Europa. Red Devils akan meladeni Partizan Belgrade di kandang.
text:
Bournemouth vs Manchester United Results: Score 1-0
02 Nov 2019, 21:31 by Bola.net
Bola.net - Manchester United (MU) is experiencing an anticlimax. After winning three consecutive wins in all competitions, MU finally collapsed. Bournemouth forced them home empty-handed.
7th MU ranks 9th Bournemouth in Vitality Stadium in Week 11 of the Premier League 2019/20, Saturday (11/02/2019). MU surrendered 0-1 by a single goal Joshua King in 45 minutes.
In the three previous matches, which are also away games, Manchester United beat Partizan Belgrade 1-0 in the Europa League, Norwich City 3-1 in the Premier League, and Chelsea 2-1 in the last 16 of the Carabao Cup.
However, there was no fourth straight win. Next, in the middle of the week, MU will play in the Europa League. The Red Devils will take on Partizan Belgrade at home.
